{"tid":1999235,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"袁國勇：防疫放寬後，市民不再合作戴口罩並再爆發疫情，可能要有罰錢措施","createTime":"2020-05-03T04:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-03T05:42:24.000Z","uid":37112,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2c591ba897a4000239c0d8880473b367cf20218f","tid":1999235,"uid":37112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523977-20200503.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523977-20200503.htm&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgp1eSlELYVUX4DDX6cHIoDA%3D&h=f642da11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1523977-20200503.htm&h=20f9cd53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1523977-20200503.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇透露，政府將會全民派發可重用口罩。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇說，創新及科技局常任秘書長蔡淑嫻早前向他表示，政府將全民派口罩，該款口罩可清洗 60次以及可更換裡面的過濾層，他形容是「德政」。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇說，相比全球，香港的防控特式就是全民佩戴口罩，早前發生的本地群組感染都是無口罩環境下發生，例如食肆、酒吧及健身中心等，認為佩戴口罩很重要。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">至於應否立法規定市民佩戴口罩，他認為市民自律及互相提醒較理想，但如果防疫措施放寬後，市民不再合作戴口罩，並再爆發疫情，就可能要有罰錢的措施。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c98b708e0a2e5af3fa18d06715b82cdc42b69af9","tid":1999235,"uid":118520,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:51:42.000Z","msg":"零確診先黎派口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc482a880be5662e291a3641ea600bc0d788b93a","tid":1999235,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T04:53:03.000Z","msg":"又死出嚟口交"},{"pid":"625228b09e141a68009291ca25233b1d6251f357","tid":1999235,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"港共只會限聚去方便打壓，而唔會強制公眾地方戴口罩，因為都係有政治目的"},{"pid":"c446867d9ce965ad887a6f4e0019c11315633c8b","tid":1999235,"uid":54104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:10:39.000Z","msg":"嚴重果時唔出呢啲<br />\n開始放援先搞呢d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0a7976d915f929f05dcb2cd01e7a50e48cd3691","tid":1999235,"uid":52876,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:13:58.000Z","msg":"誇大疫情造成經濟損失，有公司裁員又使唔使罰？"},{"pid":"bbc669b4e9509ab420e969bc3d6bda55773084cb","tid":1999235,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"好事黎，藍絲一齊蒙面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9eafc3a0c4ccf86e9a5fc6c6d91b99531245e2","tid":1999235,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"好多口罩廠開左，政府要幫手消耗口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0491437f0f49b07b40c725d45737f15ad1513889","tid":1999235,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T05:42:24.000Z","msg":"又出嚟鳩up"}]}